;sns=em\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2j9RqljSJAQ%26sns%3Dem&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b3c475da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j9RqljSJAQ&amp;sns=em</a>&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em<br />\n<br />\n香港渣車<br />\n保護自己大於一切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老實實，要比較就公平啲，<br />\n您攞e class 5系 黎比一定冇得比，<br />\n<br />\n但同日本d車仔比肯定硬淨好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撞車都要指定車款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我建議佢買車時考慮埋車輛安全性啫<br />\n<br />\nSmart for two 新款夠硬淨唔代表意外發生時你唔受重傷<br />\n<br />\n你喺香港渣得幾defensive 都避免唔到馬路炸彈"},{"pid":"babf8202a9d8891eaee2681a03fe64e7675887ba","tid":115452,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新 smart forfour 幾靚<br />\n又唔怕得兩個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRenault Twingo黎<br />\n我情願Renault自己出番</blockquote><br />\n代理無入嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廿萬又要型格又要有牌子得佢</blockquote><br />\n好拿貴喎咁既價咁既馬力<br />\nBrabus版仲要接近30個"},{"pid":"8ea8a4efa9f9ad2ccb010b22057051c83dad4a83","tid":115452,"uid":23196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j9RqljSJAQ&amp;sns=em\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2j9RqljSJAQ%26sns%3Dem&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b3c475da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j9RqljSJAQ&amp;sns=em</a>&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em<br />\n<br />\n香港渣車<br />\n保護自己大於一切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老實實，要比較就公平啲，<br />\n您攞e class 5系 黎比一定冇得比，<br />\n<br />\n但同日本d車仔比肯定硬淨好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撞車都要指定車款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我建議佢買車時考慮埋車輛安全性啫<br />\n<br />\nSmart for two 新款夠硬淨唔代表意外發生時你唔受重傷<br />\n<br />\n你喺香港渣得幾defensive 都避免唔到馬路炸彈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話要指定車款去比，只係想講好多野都係相對既<br />\n<br />\n就係有好多人都覺得細細架，一撞就入晒，<br />\n<br />\n但事實係佢個tridion 設計有啲料到，<br />\n<br />\n對比日本d車仔(fit/jazz嗰類) 可以話硬淨d<br />\n<br />\n但您係要攞黎同啲中型房車比，咁一定冇咁安全<br />\n<br />\n撞頭計超碼已經冇左引擎位做緩衝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話您提人要考慮安全性係錯<br />\n但出一架車個個人都有自已唔同既諗法/需要<br />\n唔通人人揸架大房車先叫安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自身以外既因素您避得幾多<br />\n唔揸車行路一樣可以有意外"},{"pid":"7112e15315245da8f6c43ae5da214300628a6574","tid":115452,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j9RqljSJAQ&amp;sns=em\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2j9RqljSJAQ%26sns%3Dem&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b3c475da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j9RqljSJAQ&amp;sns=em</a>&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em&amp;sns=em<br />\n<br />\n香港渣車<br />\n保護自己大於一切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老實實，要比較就公平啲，<br />\n您攞e class 5系 黎比一定冇得比，<br />\n<br />\n但同日本d車仔比肯定硬淨好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撞車都要指定車款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我建議佢買車時考慮埋車輛安全性啫<br />\n<br />\nSmart for two 新款夠硬淨唔代表意外發生時你唔受重傷<br />\n<br />\n你喺香港渣得幾defensive 都避免唔到馬路炸彈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話要指定車款去比，只係想講好多野都係相對既<br />\n<br />\n就係有好多人都覺得細細架，一撞就入晒，<br />\n<br />\n但事實係佢個tridion 設計有啲料到，<br />\n<br />\n對比日本d車仔(fit/jazz嗰類) 可以話硬淨d<br />\n<br />\n但您係要攞黎同啲中型房車比，咁一定冇咁安全<br />\n<br />\n撞頭計超碼已經冇左引擎位做緩衝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話您提人要考慮安全性係錯<br />\n但出一架車個個人都有自已唔同既諗法/需要<br />\n唔通人人揸架大房車先叫安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自身以外既因素您避得幾多<br />\n唔揸車行路一樣可以有意外</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}